  "title": "Video by hiddenjemmmig",
  "description": "One of the best SUPPER and dinner spots in Singapore! 🤌🏼 I had my first ever frog 🐸 leg porridge here and never looked back! Close to 10x here and the food is always good!! What you should order: \n🥣 Claypot Porridge \n🐸 Claypot Frogleg \n🥚 Cai Po Omelette \n🥗 Kailan / Kangkong \n🤤 Sambal Stingray (its not very spicy!) \n📌 Hong Chang Frog Porridge and BBQ Fish (2 Braddell Rd, Singapore 359895) #sghiddengems #sghiddenfood #sgfoodie #sgsupper #sgfood #sgwheretoeat #sgwhattoeat #sgeats #sgmakandiary",
